=\"#000\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg>\n      </div>\n      <h3 style=\"font-family: var(--font-inter); font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--color-midnight-ink); margin: 0;\">Timelines</h3>\n      <p style=\"font-family: var(--font-inter); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.6; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--color-soft-graphite); margin: 0;\">Visualize your project schedule with elegant timeline views designed for creative workflows.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding: 32px 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px;\">\n      <div style=\"width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1.5px solid var(--color-midnight-ink); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: var(--color-greige-canvas);\">\n        <svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M3 5h14M3 10h10M3 15h6\" stroke=\"#000\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg>\n      </div>\n      <h3 style=\"font-family: var(--font-inter); font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--color-midnight-ink); margin: 0;\">Briefs & Docs</h3>\n      <p style=\"font-family: var(--font-inter); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.6; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--color-soft-graphite); margin: 0;\">Store project briefs, creative direction, and documentation alongside the work it relates to.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
